                        Donnelly
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1948v09</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d107</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">107</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1948-11-27T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1948-11-27T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-11-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-11-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="107" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d107">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">831.00/11–2748: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Venezuela</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Donnelly</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">us urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-11-27">November 27,
                            1948</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>906. Caracas quiet this morning with business returning normal, some sporadic
                    shooting last night but much less than previous nights, horse races to be
                    resumed today and bull fight tomorrow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Donnelly</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
